These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
7 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig, fish, goat, ferret, goldfish, turtle
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: reggae, gospel, electronic, dubstep, funk, metal, indie
 1. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
 2. the owner of the goat is not the fan metal##6
 3. the fan reggae is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 4. the fan indie is somewhere to the right of the fan funk##5
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
 6. the fan reggae is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the fan gospel##7
 8. the fan gospel is on the left of the fan indie##1
 9. the fan dubstep is somewhere between the owner of the ferret and the fan electronic##7
10. the fan electronic is on the left or right of the fan reggae##3
11. the fan funk is on the far left##1
12. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the fan indie##5
13. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
14. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
15. the owner of the ferret is the fan gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Pet          | fish    | hamster    | guinea-pig | goldfish | goat | ferret    | turtle |
| Music-Genre   | funk | reggae | electronic  | metal   | dubstep    | gospel | indie |

