.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, cola, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, lemonade, milk, mirinda
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, martial-arts, sports, thriller, musical, crime, horror
 1. the person watching crime movies is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking cola##7
 2. the person watching horror movies is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
 6. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person watching sports movies##7
 7. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking cola##7
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
10. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
11. the person watching crime movies is not the person drinking mirinda##6
12. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
13. the person watching musical movies is between the person watching thriller movies and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage    | mirinda  | iced-tea | milk | hot-chocolate | water     | lemonade | cola  |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | crime | martial-arts  | horror  | musical | thriller      | comedy |

