.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-16::.
7 different pets are kept: hamster, turtle, cat, ferret, pony, horse, dog
The people have 7 different jobs:  architect, pilot, software-developer, teacher, accountant, social-worker, coach
 1. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the accountant and the teacher##7
 2. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the pilot##3
 3. the coach is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the pony##2
 4. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the software-developer##5
 5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 6. the architect is on the left or right of the teacher##3
 7. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
 8. the social-worker is the owner of the ferret##1
 9. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the accountant##5
10. the coach is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
11. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
12. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
13. the architect is somewhere between the owner of the ferret and the teacher##7
14. the owner of the pony is the pilot##1
15. the coach is the owner of the hamster##1
16. the coach is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
17. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
18. the architect is on the right of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2    |      3       |   4    |     5      |    6    |     7     |
| Pet       | horse | hamster | pony | dog | ferret     | turtle | cat  |
| Job   | software-developer  | coach   | pilot   | accountant | social-worker | architect    | teacher |

