.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-17::.
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, american, malaysian, japanese, polish, indian, argentine
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: daisy, lily, aconite, daffodil, marigold, poppy, orchid
 1. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the american##5
 2. the japanese is on the left of the indian##1
 3. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere between the person who growsaconite and the person who growsorchid##7
 4. the australian is not the person who growsaconite##6
 5. the japanese is somewhere to the right of the person who growsmarigold##5
 6. the australian is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
 7. the australian is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
 8. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4
 9. the australian is in an odd position##4
10. the person who growsdaisy is not the american##6
11. the person who growsaconite is the japanese##1
12. the malaysian is on the far left##1
13. the argentine is not the person who growsorchid##6
14. the person who growslily is the argentine##1
15. the japanese is in an even position##4
16. the american is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
17. the person who growspoppy is somewhere between the argentine and the person who growsaconite##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |       2        |      3      |        4        |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | american     | argentine | polish         | australian | japanese | indian |
| Flower     | daffodil | orchid | lily   | poppy | marigold    | aconite      | daisy |

