.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-18::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  entrepreneur, engineer, librarian, chef, doctor, manager, police-officer
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: tulip, zinnia, rose, orchid, aconite, poppy, marigold
 1. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5
 2. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
 3. the doctor is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
 4. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
 5. the doctor is not the person who growsorchid##6
 6. the manager is somewhere to the left of the engineer##5
 7. the doctor is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
 8. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
10. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
11. the person who growszinnia is not the entrepreneur##6
12. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4
13. the person who growstulip is not the librarian##6
14. the person who growsaconite is the librarian##1
15. the person who growspoppy is not the entrepreneur##6
16. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
17. the entrepreneur is somewhere between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsorchid##7
18. the doctor is somewhere to the right of the engineer##5
19. the person who growsrose is between the chef and the person who growsaconite##2
20. the chef is not the person who growspoppy##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7    |
| Job         | librarian  | manager | chef   | engineer | doctor    | entrepreneur | police-officer |
| Flower   | aconite | rose  | zinnia | tulip  | poppy | marigold    | orchid |

