.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-19::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, aristoff, alhambra, davidoff, vegafina, havana, dunhill
There are 7 different favourite beverages: mirinda, fanta, 7up, juice, iced-tea, coffee, sprite
 1. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the vegafina-smoker##5
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
 3. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
 4. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
 5. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 6. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the dunhill-smoker##7
 7. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
 8. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
 9. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
10. the havana-smoker is in an even position##4
11. the davidoff-smoker is on the far right##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
13. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the havana-smoker##5
14. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
15. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
16. the person drinking juice is not the davidoff-smoker##6
17. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
18. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the dunhill-smoker and the person drinking coffee##7
19. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3     |      4       |     5     |     6     |     7      |
| Cigar   | dunhill | havana   | vegafina | alhambra | cain | aristoff | davidoff |
| Beverage   | 7up      | juice | mirinda | iced-tea    | sprite      | coffee  | fanta    |

