.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, milk, juice, water, almond-milk, soy-milk
There are 7 different favourite colors: blood-red, lavender, light-blue, green, brown, blue, turquise
 1. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 3. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person who likes green##7
 4. the person who likes blue is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
 6. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 7. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 9. the person who likes blood-red is the person drinking water##1
10. the person who likes green is the person drinking juice##1
11. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
12. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
13. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
14. the person who likes brown is the person drinking soy-milk##1
15. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
16. the person who likes green is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
17. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
18. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blue##5
19. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |  3   |    4     |    5    |      6       |    7    |
| Beverage       | almond-milk | juice | milk | sprite | water | soy-milk | coffee |
| Color   | turquise    | green | light-blue  | lavender      | blood-red    | brown         | blue    |

 